text: Jalal Bazargan-Vali (born 23 December 1939) is an Iranian gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:Iranian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Iran Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
